727674f-a.text:
Parsons Boulevard, north from near Willets Point Boulevard, showing the entrance to the village of Whitestone. The sign on the left reads: Welcome to Whitestone -- Follow the Arrows and See the Town. The Boulevard is the former Fourth Avenue.
-P.L. Sperr  April, 1927

727675f-a.text:
Parsons Boulevard, at the S.E. corner of Willets Point Boulevard, showing a tree nursery and hot houses, one of a group of about seven or eight located in this area. The view
is across the Old Country Club Golf links.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
